summary: Another retexture for a coin. Somewhat similar to coin from Morrowind.
descriptionHtml:
Made retexture for a coin. I tried make it similar to coin from Morrowind. Just not as green. :P

Coin is trying to be similar to Morrowind coin, though there is no text on coin, because couldn't see what the text in Morrowind one said.
Check comparsion on images.

This is vanilla size texture though. Maybe making better later, maybe not..
